  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      As the effect of statin use before the angiography to prevent contrast induced nephropathy
      (CIN) is not well-known, the aim of the current study is to assess the effect of atorvastatin
      on prevention of CIN in patients undergoing coronary angiography.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
