    <measure>Contrast induced nephropathy (CIN) incidence</measure>
    <time_frame>48 hours after the procedure</time_frame>
    <description>CIN is determined as an increase in post-procedural serum creatinine of &gt; 0.5 mg/dl or &gt; 25% from baseline in the absence of any other causes</description>
